* [Configuring <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %>](https://docs.pivotal.io/application-service/<%= vars.current_major_version.sub('.','-') %>/operating/configure-pas.html).
* [Installing <%= vars.k8s_runtime_abbr %> on Azure](https://docs.pivotal.io/tkgi/1-9/installing-cli.html).
